\\bar{n}_0,\\bar{n}_0,0)$, where $\\bar{n}_0=\\frac{1}{|\\Omega|}\\int_{\\Omega}n_0$\nand $C_N$ is the best Poincar\\'{e} constant. To the best of our knowledge,\nthere are the first results on asymptotic behavior of the system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Nov 2019 10:51:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Dec 2019 08:27:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-23"}
